%% Guardrails Detectors - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant LJ as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant BI as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM / LLM Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Model as Local Model Files<br/>(Mounted Volume)
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>Scraper

    Note over Orchestrator,Model: Flow 1: HuggingFace Content Analysis

    Orchestrator->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext, No Auth
    HF->>Model: Load model from MODEL_DIR<br/>Filesystem access
    Model-->>HF: Model artifacts
    HF->>HF: Run inference<br/>(AutoModelForSequenceClassification)
    HF-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 2: LLM Judge Evaluation

    Orchestrator->>LJ: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext, Header: detector_id
    LJ->>vLLM: Forward evaluation prompt<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API key (optional)
    vLLM-->>LJ: LLM evaluation response
    LJ-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]

    Orchestrator->>LJ: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>HTTP plaintext, Header: detector_id
    LJ->>vLLM: Forward generation evaluation<br/>with prompt context
    vLLM-->>LJ: LLM evaluation response
    LJ-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse

    Note over Orchestrator,BI: Flow 3: Built-in Detection (Regex/FileType/Custom)

    Orchestrator->>BI: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext, No Auth
    BI->>BI: Run registered detectors<br/>(regex, file-type, custom)
    BI-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]

    Note over Prom,BI: Flow 4: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    Prom->>HF: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP plaintext
    HF-->>Prom: trustyai_guardrails_* counters
    Prom->>LJ: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP plaintext
    LJ-->>Prom: trustyai_guardrails_* counters
    Prom->>BI: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP plaintext
    BI-->>Prom: trustyai_guardrails_* counters
